    {
      "parameters": {
        "promptType": "define",
        "text": "=Analyze the online presence of this company:\n\nCompany Name: {{ $json.company_name }}\nDomain: {{ $json.domain }}\nWebsite: {{ $json.website }}\nIndustry: Coffee Shop\nLocation: {{ $json.city }}, {{ $json.state }}\n\nBased on the company name and domain, provide:\n\n1. **website_description**: A 1-sentence description of what their website likely contains (e.g., \"Coffee shop website featuring menu, locations, and online ordering\")\n\n2. **has_contact_form**: Would a company like this typically have a contact form on their website? (true/false/null)\n\n3. **has_social_media**: Would they likely have social media presence? (true/false)\n\n4. **likely_technologies**: What 2-3 technologies might they use? (e.g., WordPress, Shopify, Square, Instagram)\n\n5. **online_maturity**: Rate their digital presence: \"basic\" (just info), \"moderate\" (has some features), or \"advanced\" (e-commerce, app, etc.)\n\nReturn ONLY this JSON format:\n{\n  \"website_description\": \"one sentence description\",\n  \"has_contact_form\": true/false/null,\n  \"has_social_media\": true/false,\n  \"likely_technologies\": [\"tech1\", \"tech2\"],\n  \"online_maturity\": \"basic/moderate/advanced\"\n}",
        "hasOutputParser": true,
        "options": {
          "systemMessage": "You are a website and online presence analyst. You research companies' digital footprint and make intelligent assessments about their online presence based on their name, domain, and industry. Be concise and accurate."
        }
      },
